<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: The remnants of the monolith which linked our world to the void lie broken. The twisted patterns that once writhed across its surface are now motionless. You can study the broken stones to gain further knowledge of the void phenomena. -->
  <Disrupted.monolithDescription>连接我们世界与虚空的巨石残骸已经破碎。曾蔓延蠕动于其表面的扭曲纹路现如今安静了下来。你可以通过调查这些碎石，进一步了解虚空异象。</Disrupted.monolithDescription>
  <!-- EN: collapsed monolith -->
  <Disrupted.monolithLabel>坍塌巨石</Disrupted.monolithLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: Level 4: Awakened -->
  <Embraced.levelInspectText>等级4：完全唤醒</Embraced.levelInspectText>
  <!-- EN: void monolith -->
  <Embraced.monolithLabel>虚空巨石</Embraced.monolithLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: The void has awoken. The gate is open. The darkness of the void rushes into our reality, manifested from a vast mind of endless rage. -->
  <Gleaming.extraQuestDescription>虚空已被唤醒，连接两个世界的心灵通道开启了。虚空无尽的黑暗涌入了我们的现实中，自那被无尽愤怒充斥的超凡智能中显现。</Gleaming.extraQuestDescription>
  <!-- EN: Level 4: Awakened -->
  <Gleaming.levelInspectText>等级4：完全唤醒</Gleaming.levelInspectText>
  <!-- EN: void monolith -->
  <Gleaming.monolithLabel>虚空巨石</Gleaming.monolithLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: investigate {0} -->
  <Inactive.activateFloatMenuText>调查{0}</Inactive.activateFloatMenuText>
  <!-- EN: Send a colonist to investigate the monolith. -->
  <Inactive.activateGizmoDescription>派遣一名殖民者调查巨石。</Inactive.activateGizmoDescription>
  <!-- EN: investigate -->
  <Inactive.activateGizmoText>调查</Inactive.activateGizmoText>
  <!-- EN: Send a colonist to investigate the monolith. -->
  <Inactive.activateQuestText>派遣一名殖民者调查巨石。</Inactive.activateQuestText>
  <!-- EN: Twisting lines carved into the surface form a disturbing pattern. -->
  <Inactive.levelInspectText>巨石表面雕刻着扭曲的纹路，交汇形成了一副骇人的图案。</Inactive.levelInspectText>
  <!-- EN: Can be investigated now. -->
  <Inactive.monolithCanBeActivatedText>现在可以调查。</Inactive.monolithCanBeActivatedText>
  <!-- EN: fallen monolith -->
  <Inactive.monolithLabel>倒伏巨石</Inactive.monolithLabel>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has been sent to investigate the monolith. -->
  <Inactive.pawnSentToActivateMessage>已派遣{PAWN_nameDef}前去调查巨石。</Inactive.pawnSentToActivateMessage>
  
  <!-- EN: Attuning the monolith -->
  <Stirring.activatableLetterLabel>调谐巨石</Stirring.activatableLetterLabel>
  <!-- EN: You now have sufficient knowledge of void-related phenomena to attune the void monolith and further open its psychic conduit.\n\nThis will draw the attention of more dangerous anomalous entities. -->
  <Stirring.activatableLetterText>你现在已经掌握了足够的与虚空异象相关的知识，可以调谐虚空巨石，进一步开启它的心灵通道。\n\n这将吸引更为危险的异常实体。</Stirring.activatableLetterText>
  <!-- EN: As the monolith twisted and changed, {PAWN_nameDef} was overcome with a horrifying vision. In an instant, {PAWN_pronoun} understood.\n\nThe monolith is a doorway, just barely cracked open now. Something dark beyond imagination stirs on the other side, seeping into our reality.\n\nTerrified but excited, {PAWN_nameDef} is convinced {PAWN_pronoun} can learn more if given the time to study the monolith.\n\n - Building category unlocked: Anomaly\n - Research tab unlocked: Anomaly\n - Entity codex unlocked\n - You can now study the monolith and other entities to gain Anomaly research.\n\n(*Gray)Note: You can adjust the percentage of major threats that will be Anomaly-related at any point in the storyteller settings.(/Gray) -->
  <Stirring.activatedLetterText>随着巨石的扭曲变换，{PAWN_nameDef}的精神被一种骇人的景象所征服。{PAWN_pronoun}瞬间理解了。\n\n巨石就是一扇门，现在仅仅被叩开了一角。在门的另一侧则蛰伏着无可名状的邪秽之物，正在慢慢地侵蚀着我们的现实。\n\n{PAWN_nameDef}惊恐却又兴奋，确信如果能给{PAWN_pronoun}一些时间来调查巨石，就能了解更多。\n\n - 已解锁建筑类型：异象\n - 已解锁研究选项卡：异象\n - 已解锁实体图鉴\n - 你现在可以通过研究巨石和其他实体来推进异象研究项目。</Stirring.activatedLetterText>
  <!-- EN: attune {0} -->
  <Stirring.activateFloatMenuText>调谐{0}</Stirring.activateFloatMenuText>
  <!-- EN: Send a colonist to attune the monolith.\n\nThis will attract new and more dangerous entities. -->
  <Stirring.activateGizmoDescription>派遣一位殖民者去调谐巨石。\n\n这将引来更多未知且更为危险的实体。</Stirring.activateGizmoDescription>
  <!-- EN: attune -->
  <Stirring.activateGizmoText>调谐</Stirring.activateGizmoText>
  <!-- EN: Send a colonist to attune the monolith. -->
  <Stirring.activateQuestText>派一名殖民者去调谐巨石。</Stirring.activateQuestText>
  <!-- EN: You've activated the monolith. It is a conduit for psychic energy, just barely cracked open now. A mind of incomprehensible horror stirs on the other side, and is now touching our world.\n\nThe monolith seems to be partly active, and there seems to be no way to shut it down. To learn more you must activate it further, which will require some special research. -->
  <Stirring.extraQuestDescription>你已激活巨石。这是一条充斥着心灵能量的通道，且仅仅只是被叩开了一角。在另一端，蛰伏着无以名状的恐惧之物，正蠢蠢欲动，触及我们的世界。\n\n巨石看起来只有部分被激活了，而且似乎无法关闭。若想要了解更多信息，则必须进一步激活它，这需要一些特殊的研究。</Stirring.extraQuestDescription>
  <!-- EN: Level 1: Intermittent psychic humming -->
  <Stirring.levelInspectText>等级1：间动嗡鸣</Stirring.levelInspectText>
  <!-- EN: Can be attuned now. -->
  <Stirring.monolithCanBeActivatedText>现在可进行调谐。</Stirring.monolithCanBeActivatedText>
  <!-- EN: void monolith -->
  <Stirring.monolithLabel>虚空巨石</Stirring.monolithLabel>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has been sent to attune the monolith. -->
  <Stirring.pawnSentToActivateMessage>已派遣{PAWN_nameDef}前去调谐巨石。</Stirring.pawnSentToActivateMessage>
  
  <!-- EN: The sky darkens and a malevolent hum fills the air. The monolith has begun to awaken. Your actions have attracted the attention of something beyond human understanding.\n\nSoon, structures of the void will begin manifesting into this reality. Activate the arriving void structures to fully awaken the monolith.\n\nThe first wave will appear shortly. Prepare yourself. -->
  <VoidAwakened.activatedLetterText>天空暗了下来，空气中弥漫着邪恶的低语。巨石已经开始渐渐苏醒。你的行动引起了某种超出人类认知存在的注意。\n\n很快，虚空结构将降临于现实中。激活这些虚空结构，以将巨石完全唤醒。\n\n第一波很快就会出现。请做好准备。</VoidAwakened.activatedLetterText>
  <!-- EN: The void has awoken. The gate is open. The darkness of the void rushes into our reality, manifested from a vast mind of endless rage. -->
  <VoidAwakened.extraQuestDescription>巨石已被唤醒，连接两个世界的心灵通道已被开启。虚空的黑暗涌入了我们的现实中，而源头正是那蕴含无尽愤怒的暗黑超凡智能。</VoidAwakened.extraQuestDescription>
  <!-- EN: Level 3: Awakening -->
  <VoidAwakened.levelInspectText>等级3：渐醒时分</VoidAwakened.levelInspectText>
  <!-- EN: void monolith -->
  <VoidAwakened.monolithLabel>虚空巨石</VoidAwakened.monolithLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: Awakening the monolith -->
  <Waking.activatableLetterLabel>唤醒巨石</Waking.activatableLetterLabel>
  <!-- EN: You now have enough knowledge of dark phenomena to fully awaken the void monolith, opening a two-way conduit to the void.\n\nBe warned - once you begin awakening the void monolith, there is no going back. The process will shroud the region in unnatural darkness and manifest waves of horrifying entities.\n\nMake sure your colony is well-lit and well-prepared. -->
  <Waking.activatableLetterText>你现在已经掌握了足够多的关于异象的知识，可以完全唤醒虚空巨石，在两个世界间开启一条双向的心灵通道。\n\n请注意：一旦开始唤醒虚空巨石，就没有回头路了。整片区域将被异常黑暗所笼罩，骇人的实体将如潮水般袭来。\n\n请确保你的殖民地照明充足，准备充分。</Waking.activatableLetterText>
  <!-- EN: Attuning the monolith caused it to twist and grow once more. As it did, {PAWN_nameDef} caught a glimpse of what lurks beyond. {PAWN_pronoun} understood.\n\nThe monolith is a doorway, opened wider by your actions. On the other side, {PAWN_nameDef} sensed an inhuman intelligence of vast complexity and endless rage. The dark machine god is stirring, and its physical influence will grow.\n\n - New entities are now discoverable. -->
  <Waking.activatedLetterText>通过调谐巨石，它愈为扭曲，再次生长。随着这一变化，{PAWN_nameDef}得以瞥见隐藏在那之后的东西。{PAWN_pronoun}终于完全理解了。\n\n巨石即为一扇门，你所做的便是将这扇门逐渐打开。另一方面，{PAWN_nameDef}感知到了某个高深莫测、蕴含无尽愤怒的非人存在。那暗黑超凡智能正蠢蠢欲动，它对现实的物质层面影响将进一步加大。\n\n - 现在可以发现新的实体。</Waking.activatedLetterText>
  <!-- EN: awaken {0} -->
  <Waking.activateFloatMenuText>唤醒{0}</Waking.activateFloatMenuText>
  <!-- EN: Send a colonist to wake the monolith. The psychic signature will be detectable for hundreds of miles and attract all manner of horrors. Make sure you are prepared.\n\nOnce fully awakened, the monolith will provide a direct link to the void. -->
  <Waking.activateGizmoDescription>派遣一名殖民者去唤醒巨石。数百英里范围内都能探测到这种心灵信号，并会吸引各种骇人的惊惧之物，请确保你的殖民地准备充分。\n\n一旦巨石被完全唤醒，它将使现实与虚空直接相连。</Waking.activateGizmoDescription>
  <!-- EN: awaken -->
  <Waking.activateGizmoText>唤醒</Waking.activateGizmoText>
  <!-- EN: Send a colonist to awaken the monolith. -->
  <Waking.activateQuestText>派一名殖民者去唤醒巨石。</Waking.activateQuestText>
  <!-- EN: The monolith is a conduit to the void where a dark superintelligence processes endless vast dreams of rage and hate. You opened the conduit and it is now partially active. If you activate it further you can find a way to close it - or harness its power. -->
  <Waking.extraQuestDescription>巨石是连接现实与虚空的心灵通道。在那虚空中蛰伏着一个暗黑超凡智能，司掌着憎恶与愤怒的无垠之梦。巨石目前处于部分激活状态。如果你进一步激活它，也许就能找到将其关闭的方法——或者反过来利用它的力量。</Waking.extraQuestDescription>
  <!-- EN: Level 2: Pulsing with psychic energy -->
  <Waking.levelInspectText>等级2：心灵脉动</Waking.levelInspectText>
  <!-- EN: Can be awakened now. -->
  <Waking.monolithCanBeActivatedText>现在可以唤醒。</Waking.monolithCanBeActivatedText>
  <!-- EN: void monolith -->
  <Waking.monolithLabel>虚空巨石</Waking.monolithLabel>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has been sent to awaken the monolith. -->
  <Waking.pawnSentToActivateMessage>已派遣{PAWN_nameDef}前去唤醒巨石。</Waking.pawnSentToActivateMessage>
  
